name: Simple life
body:
This is simple realization of math game - Life.
It allow you to define game grid, seeds it with life and then iterate it step by step, and watch what happens with it thru generations.

![Screenshot](https://github.com/SkyRus99/simple_life/blob/master/screen.png?raw=true)
